# Design System (`@repo/design-system`)

Shared shadcn/ui component library. Apps import primitives — do not fork one-off copies in `apps/app`. App usage: `frontend-app.mdc`.

## Package boundaries

| Export | Use for |
|--------|---------|
| `@repo/design-system` | Primitives, blocks, `DesignSystemProvider`, `cn`, recipes |
| `@repo/design-system/lib/utils` | `cn()` helper without pulling full barrel |
| `@repo/design-system/lib/fonts` | Geist font setup in root layouts |
| `@repo/design-system/styles/globals.css` | Design tokens and Tailwind theme |
| `@repo/design-system/tokens/*` | Token JSON and usage policy (Storybook/governance) |
| `@repo/design-system/contracts/*` | Governance contracts (tooling only) |
| `@repo/design-system/registries/*` | Registry lookups (tooling only) |

**Do not import** `@repo/design-system/components/ui/*` outside `packages/design-system` (internal shadcn source). **Do not import** `@repo/design-system/components/afenda-ui/*` or `@repo/design-system/components/blocks/*` — those paths are not stable package exports; use the barrel.

## Implementation rules

- Add components via shadcn CLI: `npx shadcn@latest add [component] -c packages/design-system`
- Update all components: `pnpm bump-ui`
- Use semantic tokens (`bg-primary`, `text-muted-foreground`) — not ad-hoc hex in components
- Primitives under `components/ui/` are **protected** — hook asks before edits (`agent-discipline.mdc`)

## App wiring pattern

```tsx
import { Button, cn } from '@repo/design-system'

export function ActionBar({ className }: { className?: string }) {
  return (
    <div className={cn('flex gap-2', className)}>
      <Button variant="primary">Save</Button>
    </div>
  )
}
```

Keep app-specific layout in `apps/app` — extend design-system only when the pattern is reusable.

## Anti-patterns

```tsx
// ❌ Copy-paste Button into apps/app for a one-off variant
// ❌ Hard-coded colors bypassing tokens
<button className="bg-[#3b82f6]">Save</button>
// ❌ Deep imports not in package.json exports
import { Button } from '@repo/design-system/components/afenda-ui/button'

// ✅ Compose from design-system barrel + Tailwind tokens
<Button variant="default">Save</Button>
```

## Verification

```bash
pnpm --filter @repo/design-system typecheck
pnpm --filter storybook typecheck   # when stories cover changed components
```
